You are editing an educational animation framework project.

Rules:
- New scenes must be single-file implementations: src/implementations/<id>.impl.tsx
- Never create implementation subfolders under src/implementations/
- Prefer running: npm run new:implementation -- --id <id> --title "<Title>"
- Keep metadata + stage narrative + camera + timeline + visuals in one file
- Preserve white canvas mode and readable labels
- Keep compatibility with toolbar controls and recording
- After changes, run npm run lint && npm run build

